title: A Review of Episode 1207 Dave Attell and Jeff Ross
description:
Both these guys are comedy standup legends. They have a new Netflix special out called Bumping Mics. It’s a 3 parter and is fantastic if you’re into standup comedy. They have been friends with Joe for many years so this conversation was just great. I love to review these types of podcasts the most.

Enjoy my review folks!
